      "content": "<strong>Only Aphrodite, Hephaestus&#x27;s exwife, knows how to free the character, so they desperately try to woo her</strong>. - A young pegasus wander out of the heavens and ends up on Earth. A beleiver in Greek mythology must hide the magical creature until figuring ..."
    },
    {
      "title": "10 Writing Prompts from Greek Mythology - Quixotic Quill",
      "url": "https://quixoticquill.com/2018/04/23/10-writing-prompts-from-greek-mythology/",
      "content": "Quixotic Quill shares 10 writing prompts from Greek mythology. She tells the story and then shows ways it can be adapted to make a new story. Get inspired by these myths and get writing."
    },
    {
      "title": "Creative writing inspiration: Greek mythology (part 2) — dreaming by dusk",
      "url": "https://www.dreamingbydusk.com/blog/creative-writing-inspiration-greek-mythology-part-2",
      "content": "Today I’m going to share 5 more of my favourite stories and legends from Greek mythology that I learned as a Classical Studies student. I hope you enjoy them. I hope even more that you’ll find some use for them for your creativity. Here it is again, Greek mythology as creative writing inspiration."
    }
